column5: In the last few weeks, I've been hearing ads (on the radio) promoting H2O Highway. They're pushing the 'ecologically sound' part of it. I wonder if they feel the water heating up under the ships due the the invasive species debacle. I will be writing them a little letter. This is the web site. http://www.hwyh2o.com/
I unnnerstan' it's the old Ventura Highway extension.
